# .understandignore — Unreal Engine 5.4 full-engine analysis
# Aggressive exclusions are required for the deterministic compute-batches
# script to finish; without them the import-graph clustering on the full
# UE checkout (~187k source files) does not converge.

# --- Build artifacts / generated code ---
*.generated.h
*.gen.cpp
*.pb.h
*.pb.cpp
Binaries/
Intermediate/
DerivedDataCache/
Saved/
**/Intermediate/
**/Binaries/
**/DerivedDataCache/
**/Saved/

# --- ThirdParty (external libraries, not engine source) ---
ThirdParty/
**/ThirdParty/

# --- Auxiliary directories not part of engine architecture ---
Documentation/
Extras/
Programs/
Build/
Shaders/

# --- Module/plugin resource & content subdirs (icons, samples) ---
**/Resources/
**/Content/
**/Config/Localization/

